# STOP — Read this first

Your **first action** must be to load skills. Do not write code, run commands, or answer until you have done this.

**Read from:** `.cursor/rules/<skill-name>.mdc` (symlinked to ~/.cursor/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md)

---

